1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:01,840
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,840 --> 00:00:03,510
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,510 --> 00:00:04,980
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,380 --> 00:00:09,010
Assemblyman Kwon isn't returning
our calls.

5
00:00:12,020 --> 00:00:13,620
If he wanted to pull out,

6
00:00:13,620 --> 00:00:16,650
he would've kicked up a fuss
to cancel our deal,

7
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:17,760
not just avoided our calls.

8
00:00:20,830 --> 00:00:24,860
He's watching the public's reaction
to see whether to commit or not.

9
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,930
He's weighing his options.

10
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:33,470
Assemblyman Kwon is a man
driven entirely by greed.

11
00:00:35,510 --> 00:00:36,840
Since he's blinded by greed,

12
00:00:38,140 --> 00:00:39,910
use that to lure him back in.

13
00:00:40,410 --> 00:00:42,050
If doubling it isn't enough,

14
00:00:42,250 --> 00:00:44,750
raise the stakes
and offer him triple.

15
00:00:46,480 --> 00:00:48,150
Given your resources,

16
00:00:48,490 --> 00:00:51,260
you should be able to come up
with that kind of money.

17
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:06,370
(BIT Life, President Kim Myung Hui)

18
00:01:09,410 --> 00:01:11,180
Persuade Assemblyman Kwon...

19
00:01:12,340 --> 00:01:13,340
to come back.

20
00:01:15,050 --> 00:01:18,550
Tell him
I'll triple the lobbying funds.

21
00:01:20,150 --> 00:01:21,490
I see you've made a decision.

22
00:01:22,450 --> 00:01:25,360
Since you have,
I'll do my best to help, sir.

23
00:01:29,260 --> 00:01:30,730
Park Tae Ho,

24
00:01:31,460 --> 00:01:33,630
I'm going to push you
into a trap of your own greed.

25
00:01:38,270 --> 00:01:39,970
(Employee management: Chloe Lee)

26
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:41,340
(Status: Awaiting registration)

27
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:46,610
Hold on,
something looks off over there.

28
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,650
You don't want
to get into trouble for that.

29
00:01:52,750 --> 00:01:54,420
You should look into it first.

30
00:01:55,590 --> 00:01:57,290
All right, please give me a moment.

31
00:02:26,620 --> 00:02:30,020
Delete the existing fingerprint data
and register this one instead.

32
00:02:30,090 --> 00:02:31,120
(Ready to delete)

33
00:02:31,390 --> 00:02:32,390
(Re-registering)

34
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:38,330
(Re-registering)

35
00:02:50,170 --> 00:02:51,180
(Re-registering)

36
00:02:51,210 --> 00:02:52,640
(Fingerprint Registration Complete)

37
00:03:01,090 --> 00:03:02,790
What were you doing in here?

38
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,390
Why do you have that?

39
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:13,930
I dropped it by mistake.

40
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:19,300
I'll be on my way.

41
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,910
You haven't answered my question.

42
00:03:27,580 --> 00:03:29,250
What were you doing here?

43
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:40,490
Let go of her hand.

44
00:04:00,550 --> 00:04:01,910
I thought I made myself clear.

45
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:05,650
I'm the only one
who gets to hold Chloe's hand.

46
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:08,620
I need to check something with her.

47
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,520
Move.

48
00:04:11,260 --> 00:04:12,260
Check something?

49
00:04:12,890 --> 00:04:15,990
Why? So you can waste her time
and harass her again?

50
00:04:20,230 --> 00:04:22,600
It's fine. I can just answer him.

51
00:04:24,870 --> 00:04:27,610
I came to re-register
my fingerprint.

52
00:04:27,910 --> 00:04:30,710
The scanner wouldn't read my print
when I tried to enter a secure area.

53
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:34,410
The on-duty employee wasn't here,
so I waited,

54
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:35,810
but it was taking too long.

55
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:38,680
I was about to leave
and come back later.

56
00:04:41,450 --> 00:04:42,450
There.

57
00:04:43,450 --> 00:04:44,460
Satisfied now?

58
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:50,030
Let's go. I'm sure
you have work to get back to.

59
00:04:51,730 --> 00:04:53,060
No need to waste any more time.

60
00:05:20,090 --> 00:05:21,290
What was that all about?

61
00:05:21,930 --> 00:05:23,330
Why did you come
to the security office?

62
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:27,400
Does he really know who I am?

63
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:31,700
Did he follow me there knowing
I'd re-register my fingerprint?

64
00:05:32,340 --> 00:05:34,540
That's not the point right now.

65
00:05:35,540 --> 00:05:37,480
Why was Min Jun grabbing
your wrist again?

66
00:05:38,380 --> 00:05:40,980
If your fingerprint wasn't working
and you had to re-register it,

67
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,810
you could've asked me
to go with you.

68
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,390
This is the second time
it has happened.

69
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:51,490
If I see him grab your wrist
one more time,

70
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:54,390
I'm really going to lose it.

71
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,310
Baek Jin Ju.

72
00:06:14,250 --> 00:06:16,250
Don't let anyone else find out
about you.

73
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:19,280
Especially not that jerk,
Park Min Jun.

74
00:06:24,690 --> 00:06:27,160
Is it true that Chloe requested
to re-register her fingerprint?

75
00:06:27,690 --> 00:06:30,130
Yes. I had to leave
for an urgent system check,

76
00:06:30,530 --> 00:06:33,030
so I couldn't process the request,
but she did ask.

77
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,600
I see.

78
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:38,940
Did you perhaps tell her
I asked you to pull...

79
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:42,570
her fingerprint from the database
a few hours ago?

80
00:06:42,710 --> 00:06:43,710
No, sir.

81
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:47,250
I bent the rules as a favor for you,
on your orders.

82
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,650
Of course I kept it a secret.

83
00:06:49,580 --> 00:06:52,220
Good. Keep it that way.

84
00:06:52,420 --> 00:06:53,450
Sure.

85
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:06,160
(Chloe Lee)

86
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:27,050
She was there
to re-register her fingerprint?

87
00:07:34,690 --> 00:07:36,160
You haven't answered my question.

88
00:07:36,790 --> 00:07:38,560
What were you doing here?

89
00:07:47,770 --> 00:07:50,070
But why was she trembling?

90
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:55,910
This just makes me
even more suspicious.

91
00:08:02,690 --> 00:08:04,820
I changed the fingerprint data.

92
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:08,860
I think we made a mistake
in a panic.

93
00:08:09,090 --> 00:08:11,000
Even if your print is in the system,

94
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,860
they can't pull up Baek Jin Ju's...

95
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:15,100
to compare it.

96
00:08:16,470 --> 00:08:19,340
Legally,
unless it's for an investigation,

97
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:21,170
they can't release
the deceased's fingerprints.

98
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:25,240
Going to security for no reason
only raised suspicion.

99
00:08:25,810 --> 00:08:28,310
Still, it's better not to leave
any trace behind.

100
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:32,020
If Chairman Park decides
he wants to check for himself,

101
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,590
you know he'll just bend the rules.

102
00:08:35,690 --> 00:08:36,720
All right.

103
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:40,020
For now, let's just watch
how things play out and be careful.

104
00:08:40,390 --> 00:08:42,930
Sure. Now that the competition
has started,

105
00:08:42,990 --> 00:08:44,860
I'll try
to shift their attention to it.

106
00:08:58,910 --> 00:09:01,010
(Park Min Jun,
Adele's Head of Division 1)

107
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:03,750
You said you didn't want
to live in the past anymore.

108
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:07,150
You wanted
to leave Baek Jin Ju behind...

109
00:09:07,820 --> 00:09:09,890
and come to Chloe.

110
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:14,130
So, please,

111
00:09:16,530 --> 00:09:18,130
stop digging up the past.

112
00:09:23,100 --> 00:09:24,340
Enjoy your meal.

113
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,310
Triple?

114
00:10:08,180 --> 00:10:11,050
Are you offering 60 million dollars
in lobbying funds?

115
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:13,520
High risk, high reward.

116
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:16,390
Now that people are suspicious
of the deal,

117
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:19,020
we have to be more careful.

118
00:10:19,090 --> 00:10:21,330
Shouldn't the reward be
that much greater?

119
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:26,930
But Adele is under
a lot of scrutiny.

120
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:31,300
You'd pass up this opportunity
because of that?

121
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:34,410
The money that goes
to the foreign associates...

122
00:10:34,610 --> 00:10:36,910
can be the same amount as before.

123
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:41,880
The rest is all for you to take,
Assemblyman Kwon.

124
00:10:43,210 --> 00:10:45,680
The rest is all for me?

125
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:49,090
You're the most crucial person
in this deal, after all.

126
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:54,190
In that case,

127
00:10:55,090 --> 00:10:56,790
I'll think it over.

128
00:10:57,730 --> 00:10:59,500
We can't give you much time.

129
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:01,270
Please get back to me
within three days.

130
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:12,910
Is that so?

131
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,950
He'll think it over?

132
00:11:17,010 --> 00:11:21,090
It looks like he took the bait,
so now we wait.

133
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:23,820
Good work.

134
00:11:29,430 --> 00:11:31,260
Let's see.

135
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:49,850
Once I take money
out of my slush fund...

136
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:52,320
and sell off some paintings
from the gallery,

137
00:11:53,620 --> 00:11:55,690
I'll have something more reliable.

138
00:11:56,290 --> 00:11:58,020
The exclusive development rights.

139
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:01,360
That's real power.

140
00:12:15,010 --> 00:12:16,110
Right.

141
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:19,680
Did your meeting go well?

142
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:21,580
Yes, Mrs. Han.

143
00:12:24,550 --> 00:12:27,350
I asked for a favor
since we had to meet in secret.

144
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:29,150
Sorry for imposing on you again.

145
00:12:29,390 --> 00:12:31,890
Nonsense. It's no imposition at all.

146
00:12:31,990 --> 00:12:34,160
Please feel free to come by anytime.

147
00:12:34,930 --> 00:12:36,030
Thank you.

148
00:12:36,930 --> 00:12:37,930
By the way,

149
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:41,330
you previously tried
to break the deal...

150
00:12:41,330 --> 00:12:43,030
between Chairman Park
and Assemblyman Kwon,

151
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:45,900
but now it seems
you intend to use it instead.

152
00:12:47,810 --> 00:12:50,370
Is my hunch correct?

153
00:12:50,740 --> 00:12:52,840
Yes, you're right.

154
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:58,750
I even took the risk
of getting arrested to stop the deal,

155
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:02,920
but there appears to be no end
to their greed.

156
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:06,720
So they could just team up again
at any moment?

157
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:10,830
I decided it was more useful
to use the deal to my advantage...

158
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:13,400
instead of trying
to stop it every time.

159
00:13:16,370 --> 00:13:20,100
Going forward,
you have a lot on your plate.

160
00:13:20,770 --> 00:13:22,040
If you need my help,

161
00:13:22,740 --> 00:13:24,140
please don't hesitate to ask.

162
00:13:33,150 --> 00:13:35,720
Excuse me, if you're both finished,

163
00:13:35,790 --> 00:13:37,960
may I give her your gift?

164
00:13:38,490 --> 00:13:39,690
A gift?

165
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:42,830
I wanted to show
how much I appreciate all your help.

166
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:47,900
I know making hanboks must be hard,
sitting in one position for hours.

167
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:50,770
I was hoping this might help.

168
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:56,440
Even though I'm young,
I get aches and pains...

169
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:58,910
in my knees and shoulders.

170
00:13:59,010 --> 00:14:01,350
I can only imagine how you feel.

171
00:14:01,410 --> 00:14:04,480
Take this, and even your dry,
overworked hands...

172
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:06,850
will feel as smooth as silk.

173
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:09,650
In that case,

174
00:14:10,290 --> 00:14:12,260
I can't take this alone.

175
00:14:12,460 --> 00:14:14,020
You two must have some with me.

176
00:14:15,030 --> 00:14:17,600
Then our dear boss should go first.

177
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,800
I'm always worried you'll blow away
in the wind.

178
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:22,400
You have some first.

179
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,000
Thanks.

180
00:14:43,590 --> 00:14:45,690
(Adele)

181
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:49,160
Did you set up the meeting
with Producer Shin?

182
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:52,900
He said he's coming by the office
this afternoon to see the products.

183
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:55,870
Why?
Would you like to join the meeting?

184
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:58,540
Wouldn't that put me
at a disadvantage?

185
00:14:59,270 --> 00:15:00,800
I'm going to meet him on my own,

186
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:03,070
so let's just handle
our own business.

187
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,850
She's meeting him separately?

188
00:15:15,990 --> 00:15:16,990
A contract?

189
00:15:17,690 --> 00:15:19,160
I haven't decided yet,

190
00:15:19,420 --> 00:15:22,060
but Adele will present deals
from two different teams,

191
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:23,090
so I'll hear them out.

192
00:15:23,990 --> 00:15:26,330
Okay. I'll let you know
after the meeting.

193
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:43,680
Producer Shin?

194
00:15:45,180 --> 00:15:46,680
You're here for the meeting, right?

195
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:48,320
Yes.

196
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:51,390
I need to borrow you for a moment
before your meeting.

197
00:15:51,990 --> 00:15:55,460
The chairman's wife
from the Adele Group is waiting.

198
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:19,280
The woman you were with
is a married actress.

199
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:21,490
Are you two kidding me?

200
00:16:22,050 --> 00:16:23,920
She's just a close friend...

201
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:27,220
Whatever the case,
you have feelings for her.

202
00:16:27,990 --> 00:16:29,860
If these photos get out,

203
00:16:31,130 --> 00:16:33,300
things will be much harder on her.

204
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:38,700
There you go.

205
00:16:38,970 --> 00:16:41,210
Looks like you're finally
getting it.

206
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,270
Is this your first time
being blackmailed?

207
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:47,810
Think of it as a business deal,
not blackmail.

208
00:16:48,350 --> 00:16:51,620
If you choose me as your partner
for the show,

209
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:54,520
these photos will disappear
immediately.

210
00:16:57,760 --> 00:16:59,160
As for the production funding,

211
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,660
you'll be more than satisfied.

212
00:17:01,830 --> 00:17:03,160
(Brand Partnership Proposal)

213
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:18,010
Fixers these days
work incredibly fast.

214
00:17:18,510 --> 00:17:20,010
They beat me to it.

215
00:17:22,910 --> 00:17:25,780
Why isn't Hyun Jun
picking up his phone?

216
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,590
My dear Hyun Jun's love life.

217
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:32,320
I have to be the one to protect it.

218
00:17:39,660 --> 00:17:42,100
What do you mean
you can't reach Producer Shin?

219
00:17:42,170 --> 00:17:45,100
The meeting should've started,
but he didn't show up.

220
00:17:45,870 --> 00:17:47,240
He's not answering his phone either.

221
00:17:47,970 --> 00:17:50,970
Could he have gotten into
an accident on his way here?

222
00:17:55,180 --> 00:17:56,350
Hello, Producer Shin.

223
00:17:57,180 --> 00:17:59,020
I'm afraid I can't make
our appointment today.

224
00:17:59,380 --> 00:18:00,380
Actually,

225
00:18:01,190 --> 00:18:02,820
there won't be any meetings, period.

226
00:18:03,290 --> 00:18:04,290
Goodbye.

227
00:18:04,660 --> 00:18:06,420
Mr. Shin, what do you mean...

228
00:18:09,190 --> 00:18:11,560
Producer Shin just canceled
all our meetings.

229
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:14,300
I need to see him in person
and find out what's going on.

230
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,400
I'm coming with you.

231
00:18:22,970 --> 00:18:24,810
Don't forget to take
the proposal with you.

232
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:29,080
I'll get the contract drawn up
right away.

233
00:18:36,490 --> 00:18:38,020
Okay.

234
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:39,790
Game over.

235
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,260
That was way too easy.

236
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:45,500
Of course.
What'd you expect with me involved?

237
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:48,800
I spent so much money
at that agency to rush things.

238
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:51,870
You just focus on
planning your wedding.

239
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:55,170
I'm off to pull one over
on Kim Myung Hui.

240
00:18:58,740 --> 00:19:00,910
What? Where did he go?

241
00:19:02,210 --> 00:19:04,310
Seriously,
why does he keep disappearing?

242
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:07,680
Hyun Jun!

243
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:11,420
Jung Ran and Ms. Choi...

244
00:19:11,420 --> 00:19:13,520
blackmailed the producer
to sign the contract...

245
00:19:18,030 --> 00:19:20,430
Blackmail?
What are you talking about?

246
00:19:29,840 --> 00:19:32,740
Is it true
that Producer Shin was blackmailed?

247
00:19:32,810 --> 00:19:34,280
Is that why he's refusing
to meet us?

248
00:19:37,110 --> 00:19:38,180
Blackmail?

249
00:19:40,750 --> 00:19:42,850
I came to hear
how things went with Mr. Shin,

250
00:19:44,490 --> 00:19:45,990
so why am I hearing about blackmail?

251
00:19:47,020 --> 00:19:50,830
Because Mr. Shin was blackmailed,
he refused to meet Chloe.

252
00:19:51,630 --> 00:19:53,230
I bet this was Choi Yu Na's doing.

253
00:19:55,370 --> 00:19:56,830
It was her, but also...

254
00:20:05,180 --> 00:20:08,310
Oh Jung Ran got involved again,
didn't she?

255
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:15,250
You must see it now.

256
00:20:15,550 --> 00:20:19,890
This is why people who do wrong
must be punished accordingly.

257
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:23,790
Because if not,
they'll never learn their lesson.

258
00:20:24,130 --> 00:20:25,930
With no shame, they just stomp...

259
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:29,230
on their own child's heart...

260
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:31,770
and don't even think twice about it.

261
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:34,910
How does it feel
now that it's happening to you?

262
00:20:35,310 --> 00:20:39,540
Do you still think you should cover
for your mother?

263
00:20:52,460 --> 00:20:53,460
Hyun Jun!

264
00:20:58,530 --> 00:21:00,430
Don't you think
you were a bit harsh?

265
00:21:00,630 --> 00:21:02,170
Did you really...

266
00:21:02,230 --> 00:21:04,770
have to crush his pride
in front of everyone?

267
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:08,870
Why do you think
Oh Jung Ran interfered?

268
00:21:10,770 --> 00:21:11,880
It was done...

269
00:21:12,310 --> 00:21:14,610
to force my son
into a marriage he doesn't want.

270
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:18,250
She's trying to make
my son miserable...

271
00:21:19,220 --> 00:21:20,820
just to hurt me.

272
00:21:22,190 --> 00:21:25,990
In that case,
I have to return the favor.

273
00:21:28,190 --> 00:21:30,430
I don't care if she comes after me.

274
00:21:31,730 --> 00:21:33,460
But when it comes to my son,

275
00:21:34,530 --> 00:21:37,400
I won't forgive anyone
who messes with him.

276
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:48,180
He's got some nerve ditching me
when he's my chauffeur.

277
00:21:48,750 --> 00:21:50,910
Unbelievable.

278
00:21:54,950 --> 00:21:56,450
I'll give him a piece of my mind.

279
00:21:56,450 --> 00:21:57,590
Jung Ran!

280
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:03,030
Where the heck have you been?

281
00:22:03,330 --> 00:22:04,760
It's just that...

282
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,200
I did something bad.

283
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:09,800
Something bad?

284
00:22:10,430 --> 00:22:11,870
Did you crash the car?

285
00:22:11,900 --> 00:22:13,970
I should've been more careful...

286
00:22:14,870 --> 00:22:16,010
You hit someone?

287
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:18,580
No, it's not that.

288
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:24,180
- Hyun Jun.
- Hyun Jun.

289
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:27,480
What's wrong? Did something happen?

290
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:29,720
Is it true?

291
00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:32,760
Did you and Choi Yu Na...

292
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,530
blackmail Producer Shin?

293
00:22:36,390 --> 00:22:39,200
What? How did you...

294
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:43,770
- You little...
- Well, I...

295
00:22:44,530 --> 00:22:47,940
I was only going to tell Hyun Jun
so he could deal with it quietly,

296
00:22:48,410 --> 00:22:51,740
but I didn't realize Min Jun
would be in his office.

297
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:53,640
What?

298
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:56,180
So, you're saying
they know everything?

299
00:22:56,450 --> 00:22:57,550
That's right.

300
00:22:58,850 --> 00:23:00,380
They know everything.

301
00:23:02,150 --> 00:23:04,090
The woman I love...

302
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:09,160
and the man I can't stand losing to
found out everything.

303
00:23:11,730 --> 00:23:14,000
Of all people, my own mother...

304
00:23:15,500 --> 00:23:18,100
crushed my feelings
and made me look like a fool.

305
00:23:18,100 --> 00:23:19,670
They saw it firsthand.

306
00:23:22,010 --> 00:23:23,010
So what?

307
00:23:23,870 --> 00:23:26,280
As if your pathetic
and laughable feelings matter.

308
00:23:28,980 --> 00:23:30,580
My pathetic, laughable feelings?

309
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:34,480
I told you I love her.

310
00:23:36,750 --> 00:23:40,960
I told you I want this desperately.
I told you that!

311
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:44,860
How dare you raise your voice
at your mother?

312
00:23:45,630 --> 00:23:47,500
I made myself perfectly clear too.

313
00:23:48,030 --> 00:23:50,700
I will never accept
that scheming fox!

314
00:24:00,280 --> 00:24:01,410
My gosh!

315
00:24:08,620 --> 00:24:11,590
Blood! You're bleeding!

316
00:24:11,690 --> 00:24:13,190
What in the world...

317
00:24:14,560 --> 00:24:15,630
Don't belittle Chloe...

318
00:24:17,590 --> 00:24:18,660
or trivialize...

319
00:24:21,460 --> 00:24:22,700
my feelings for her.

320
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:27,270
Don't embarrass me
in front of her...

321
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:31,240
or Park Min Jun.

322
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:34,380
You...

323
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:37,980
How could you?
How could you do this to me?

324
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:40,650
All because of some worthless girl?

325
00:24:42,820 --> 00:24:43,820
Worthless?

326
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:50,260
So you still think
my feelings are a joke.

327
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,730
Hyun Jun!

328
00:25:04,040 --> 00:25:05,140
That's enough.

329
00:25:10,480 --> 00:25:11,620
Stay out of this.

330
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,750
What are you going to tell Chloe?

331
00:25:15,750 --> 00:25:17,190
She's going to be worried.

332
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:19,560
Just stop.

333
00:25:36,910 --> 00:25:37,910
Hyun Jun...

334
00:25:39,780 --> 00:25:42,780
Wait. Hyun Jun,
we need to get you to a doctor!

335
00:25:43,150 --> 00:25:44,880
Hyun Jun!

336
00:26:02,830 --> 00:26:03,830
What?

337
00:26:04,330 --> 00:26:05,840
Are you going to blame me
for this too?

338
00:26:09,610 --> 00:26:12,710
Although today,
it might be partly my fault.

339
00:26:14,810 --> 00:26:15,950
After all,

340
00:26:16,250 --> 00:26:19,050
I'm the one who just crushed
your precious son's ego.

341
00:26:24,020 --> 00:26:26,360
(Team Leader, Choi Yu Na)

342
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:41,470
Tonight, everyone's fighting,

343
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:43,570
hurting, and confused.

344
00:26:44,710 --> 00:26:47,940
It's not right that only you get
to have it easy, Choi Yu Na.

345
00:26:50,010 --> 00:26:51,480
It's only fair...

346
00:26:52,180 --> 00:26:54,150
that you suffer as much as I have.

347
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:05,160
Oh my goodness.

348
00:27:07,100 --> 00:27:08,630
- Good heavens.
- My gosh.

349
00:27:11,330 --> 00:27:13,770
What is this?

350
00:27:18,110 --> 00:27:19,180
Oh my.

351
00:27:20,580 --> 00:27:21,980
- My gosh!
- My goodness!

352
00:27:22,050 --> 00:27:23,510
It's Jin Ju!

353
00:27:23,610 --> 00:27:26,150
But how? I thought she was dead.

354
00:27:27,150 --> 00:27:28,650
Honey, oh my gosh.

355
00:27:29,520 --> 00:27:32,590
Goodness, honey,
get a hold of yourself.

356
00:27:34,460 --> 00:27:35,460
My gosh.

357
00:27:41,300 --> 00:27:42,300
What's going on?

358
00:27:42,600 --> 00:27:46,240
- It's a ghost.
- My father and I lost everything.

359
00:27:47,770 --> 00:27:50,970
And all this time, you've been
living comfortably in this house...

360
00:27:51,410 --> 00:27:52,810
without a care in the world?

361
00:27:57,380 --> 00:27:59,080
Oh my, I'm so scared.

362
00:28:00,450 --> 00:28:03,820
Why would a ghost be doing this?

363
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:06,420
What kind of grudge
could she have with us?

364
00:28:07,460 --> 00:28:09,360
What? A grudge?

365
00:28:10,390 --> 00:28:12,400
Could it be...

366
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:14,700
Is this because of what I did?

367
00:28:15,330 --> 00:28:16,330
What?

368
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:21,540
My gosh!

369
00:28:21,810 --> 00:28:26,340
Honey! Sam Sik, snap out of it!

370
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:29,710
How can you just pass out on me
in a situation like this?

371
00:28:30,210 --> 00:28:34,380
If you check out and leave me alone,
what am I supposed to do?

372
00:28:34,550 --> 00:28:37,520
I'm terrified, so snap out of it!

373
00:28:42,560 --> 00:28:45,430
By the way,
when will Ms. Choi be home?

374
00:28:46,460 --> 00:28:49,870
Oh my, I'm scared out of my mind.

375
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:52,100
Chloe?

376
00:28:53,740 --> 00:28:57,110
Yu Na! My gosh, this is terrifying.

377
00:28:57,440 --> 00:28:59,610
- Yu Na.
- What took you so long?

378
00:28:59,940 --> 00:29:01,540
I've been waiting for you.

379
00:29:05,280 --> 00:29:08,520
What are you doing,
coming to my house at this hour?

380
00:29:08,890 --> 00:29:11,690
Oh, my.
What is she talking about now?

381
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:14,620
Yu Na, have you lost your mind too?

382
00:29:14,620 --> 00:29:17,530
How are you talking to a ghost?

383
00:29:17,660 --> 00:29:21,200
Mom, you're the one
who needs to snap out of it.

384
00:29:21,630 --> 00:29:24,870
This isn't Baek Jin Ju.
It's Chloe Lee.

385
00:29:25,300 --> 00:29:26,670
She's a different person.

386
00:29:26,670 --> 00:29:27,670
What was that?

387
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,570
Chloe?

388
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:33,140
But she's the spitting image
of Jin Ju.

389
00:29:36,010 --> 00:29:38,410
Why did you have
to come here unannounced...

390
00:29:38,410 --> 00:29:39,820
and cause such a scene?

391
00:29:39,950 --> 00:29:44,020
Before this night is over,
I need to return something to you.

392
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:55,970
Yu Na, my goodness!
What do you think you're doing?

393
00:29:56,930 --> 00:29:57,930
You...

394
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:00,840
What was that?

395
00:30:02,810 --> 00:30:06,340
That's what you get
for breaking our promise.

396
00:30:07,410 --> 00:30:10,650
We promised to be friends,
to be on the same side...

397
00:30:10,710 --> 00:30:12,050
and you played dirty.

398
00:30:12,350 --> 00:30:14,020
I can't just let that slide, can I?

399
00:30:15,490 --> 00:30:17,790
Since you stabbed me in the back,

400
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:20,560
I had to
at least slap you in the face.

401
00:30:28,430 --> 00:30:30,330
How dare you mess with my son?

402
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:33,040
Why not?

403
00:30:34,370 --> 00:30:36,440
You get to go after my son,

404
00:30:37,570 --> 00:30:38,980
but I'm not allowed
to go after yours?

405
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:42,850
If you were set on trapping my son
in an unhappy marriage,

406
00:30:43,910 --> 00:30:46,780
you should've known your own son
could end up miserable too.

407
00:30:48,550 --> 00:30:49,990
If anything happens to Min Jun,

408
00:30:50,720 --> 00:30:53,160
the same thing will happen
to your son.

409
00:30:54,690 --> 00:30:56,890
He'll pay the price
for having a mother like you.

410
00:31:00,960 --> 00:31:02,330
Don't think you've won.

411
00:31:06,370 --> 00:31:10,310
You'll pay tenfold
for humiliating me today,

412
00:31:12,280 --> 00:31:13,840
and I'll get even...

413
00:31:15,580 --> 00:31:17,450
for Hyun Jun too.

414
00:31:29,060 --> 00:31:31,660
(Gemologist Kim Myung Hui
Says the Ornament Is Fake)

415
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:35,160
(Park Tae Ho)

416
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:55,790
Right.

417
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:02,490
Excuse me. Just a second.

418
00:32:03,560 --> 00:32:04,560
What is it?

419
00:32:06,400 --> 00:32:07,400
Is this...

420
00:32:08,060 --> 00:32:09,930
where Kim Dan Hui lives?

421
00:32:43,900 --> 00:32:46,700
(Pearl in Red)

422
00:32:46,970 --> 00:32:48,240
I told you to compete,

423
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:50,110
not resort to threats
or meddling with contracts.

424
00:32:50,170 --> 00:32:52,910
You shouldn't have let Hyun Jun
get involved with that vixen.

425
00:32:53,210 --> 00:32:56,180
If you'd shut them down,
I wouldn't have had to get involved!

426
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:59,080
I see you've decided to take my side
in the competition.

427
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:01,880
Don't lose.
You worked so hard for this.

428
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,120
I really hope you win.

429
00:33:03,290 --> 00:33:04,590
Okay, I will.

430
00:33:04,590 --> 00:33:07,490
Do you know someone
named Kim Dan Hui?

431
00:33:07,490 --> 00:33:09,460
What do you mean by that?

432
00:33:09,690 --> 00:33:13,230
Someone came by the house
looking for Kim Dan Hui.

433
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:15,260
Sorry?

434
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:18,200
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
